detailed_optimizations.code_changes:
将 /9.0 改为乘以预计算常量 inv9；为数组指针提供 restrict/assume_aligned；将行指针提取到局部变量以减少地址计算。例如：

const DATA_TYPE inv9 = (DATA_TYPE)1.0 / (DATA_TYPE)9.0;
for (t = 0; t < tsteps; ++t) {
  for (i = 1; i < n - 1; ++i) {
    DATA_TYPE * __restrict rowm = A[i-1];
    DATA_TYPE * __restrict row  = A[i];
    DATA_TYPE * __restrict rowp = A[i+1];
    for (j = 1; j < n - 1; ++j) {
      row[j] = (rowm[j-1] + rowm[j] + rowm[j+1]
              + row [j-1] + row [j] + row [j+1]
              + rowp[j-1] + rowp[j] + rowp[j+1]) * inv9;
    }
  }
}

若使用平坦数组，可进一步写成 DATA_TYPE * __restrict A 并手工索引 idx=i*n+j。

对 i/j 做二维 tiling，使工作集更好驻留在 L1/L2。示例：

for (t = 0; t < tsteps; ++t)
  for (ii = 1; ii < n-1; ii += Ti)
    for (jj = 1; jj < n-1; jj += Tj)
      for (i = ii; i < min(ii+Ti, n-1); ++i) {
        DATA_TYPE *rowm = A[i-1], *row = A[i], *rowp = A[i+1];
        for (j = jj; j < min(jj+Tj, n-1); ++j)
          row[j] = (rowm[j-1]+rowm[j]+rowm[j+1]+
                    row[j-1]+row[j]+row[j+1]+
                    rowp[j-1]+rowp[j]+rowp[j+1]) * inv9;
      }

Ti/Tj 需按 cache 调优，典型可从 32x64、64x64 开始。注意该优化主要改善 cache/TLB 行为，不改变依赖方向。

在 j 方向维护 3 行的滑动窗口，减少重复加载和地址计算。示意：

for (i = 1; i < n-1; ++i) {
  DATA_TYPE *rowm = A[i-1], *row = A[i], *rowp = A[i+1];
  DATA_TYPE a0=rowm[0], a1=rowm[1];
  DATA_TYPE b0=row[0],  b1=row[1];
  DATA_TYPE c0=rowp[0], c1=rowp[1];
  for (j = 1; j < n-1; ++j) {
    DATA_TYPE a2 = rowm[j+1];
    DATA_TYPE b2 = row [j+1];
    DATA_TYPE c2 = rowp[j+1];
    row[j] = (a0+a1+a2 + b0+b1+b2 + c0+c1+c2) * inv9;
    a0=a1; a1=a2; b0=b1; b1=b2; c0=c1; c1=c2;
  }
}

该形式可减少部分重复访存，但由于 row[j] 原地更新，自动向量化仍受限。

不能直接对 i/j 使用普通 OpenMP parallel for，因为存在同一步内依赖。可按 d=i+j 的波前并行：

for (t = 0; t < tsteps; ++t) {
  for (d = 2; d <= 2*(n-2); ++d) {
    #pragma omp parallel for schedule(static)
    for (i = max(1, d-(n-2)); i <= min(n-2, d-1); ++i) {
      int j = d - i;
      A[i][j] = (A[i-1][j-1] + A[i-1][j] + A[i-1][j+1]
               + A[i][j-1]   + A[i][j]   + A[i][j+1]
               + A[i+1][j-1] + A[i+1][j] + A[i+1][j+1]) * inv9;
    }
  }
}

更高效的实现通常结合 tile-wavefront：先分块，再按 tile 对角线并行，降低同步次数。

若允许改变更新顺序/数值轨迹，推荐双缓冲 Jacobi：

for (t = 0; t < tsteps; ++t) {
  for (i = 1; i < n-1; ++i)
    for (j = 1; j < n-1; ++j)
      B[i][j] = (A[i-1][j-1] + A[i-1][j] + A[i-1][j+1]
               + A[i][j-1]   + A[i][j]   + A[i][j+1]
               + A[i+1][j-1] + A[i+1][j] + A[i+1][j+1]) * inv9;
  swap(A, B);
}

若需保持 Gauss-Seidel 语义更接近，可采用红黑着色：先更新 (i+j)%2==0，再更新 (i+j)%2==1，并在每个颜色阶段并行。
